  <brief_title>Study Evaluating Pantoprazole in Adolescents With GERD</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Multicenter, Randomized, Open-Label, Single And Multiple Dose Study Of The Pharmacokinetics And Safety of Two Dose Levels of Pantoprazole Sodium Tablets In Adolescents Aged 12 Through 16 Years With A Clinical Daignosis Of GERD.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
