  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is characterize the PK profile of single and multiple doses of
      pantoprazole in adolescents aged 12 to 16 years with Gastroesophageal Reflux Disease (GERD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
